    20Ôćĺ**mdBook** is a command line tool to create books with Markdown.
    21ÔćĺIt is ideal for creating product or API documentation, tutorials, course materials or anything that requires a clean,
    22Ôćĺeasily navigable and customizable presentation.
    23Ôćĺ
    24Ôćĺ* Lightweight [Markdown] syntax helps you focus more on your content
    25Ôćĺ* Integrated [search] support
    26Ôćĺ* Color [syntax highlighting] for code blocks for many different languages
    27Ôćĺ* [Theme] files allow customizing the formatting of the output
    28Ôćĺ* [Preprocessors] can provide extensions for custom syntax and modifying content
    29Ôćĺ* [Backends] can render the output to multiple formats
    30Ôćĺ* Written in [Rust] for speed, safety, and simplicity
    31Ôćĺ* Automated testing of [Rust code samples]
    32Ôćĺ
    33ÔćĺThis guide is an example of what mdBook produces.
