for_developers/preprocessors.md
     1Ôćĺ# Preprocessors
     3ÔćĺA *preprocessor* is simply a bit of code which gets run immediately after the
     4Ôćĺbook is loaded and before it gets rendered, allowing you to update and mutate
     5Ôćĺthe book. Possible use cases are:
     6Ôćĺ
     7Ôćĺ- Creating custom helpers like `\{{#include /path/to/file.md}}`
     8Ôćĺ- Substituting in latex-style expressions (`$$ \frac{1}{3} $$`) with their
     9Ôćĺ  mathjax equivalents
    10Ôćĺ
    11ÔćĺSee [Configuring Preprocessors](../format/configuration/preprocessors.md) for more information about using preprocessors.
    12Ôćĺ
