guide/reading.md
     1Ôćĺ# Reading books
     3ÔćĺThis chapter gives an introduction on how to interact with a book produced by mdBook.
     4ÔćĺThis assumes you are reading an HTML book.
     5ÔćĺThe options and formatting will be different for other output formats such as PDF.
     6Ôćĺ
     7ÔćĺA book is organized into *chapters*.
     8ÔćĺEach chapter is a separate page.
     9ÔćĺChapters can be nested into a hierarchy of sub-chapters.
    10ÔćĺTypically, each chapter will be organized into a series of *headings* to subdivide a chapter.
    11Ôćĺ
    12Ôćĺ## Navigation
    26Ôćĺ## Top menu bar
    42Ôćĺ## Search
    54Ôćĺ## Code blocks

